summary: some of the most beautiful celebrity eyes I could find on the net. edit; now darkened.
descriptionHtml:
to install just unzip to a folder and paste into your skyrim folder, overwrite the data file when windows asks you to. the folder structure is already done.

there are more different types of human eyes but no bloodshot in this version because of that. you may get some NCP's with different coloured eyes, I couldn't do anything about that, but I prefer to have the options.
author: amorphos098
